{"tid":936511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【北角烈士】校巴司機為打擊民建聯票倉，不惜犧牲自己！","createTime":"2018-12-10T23:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T00:49:51.000Z","uid":202464,"like":14,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e31160b1cbdfefebc0e223c89b155002958555b6","tid":936511,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T23:13:58.000Z","msg":"琴日北角校巴撞人單野，校巴司機為打擊民建聯票倉，不惜深入虎穴，撲殺四名賣港奶共老人（分別為70、77、80、83歲）。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士透露，該四名老人一邊領取香港醫療券、生果金、老人綜援，一邊支持支那侵港，每次投票都支持賣港民建聯/工聯會候選人。<br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，校巴司機已成功瓦解其中兩名男廢老引蝗入港陰謀。知情人士透露，二人有意以結婚名義，協助支那女人來港蠶食港人福利，並誕下小蝗蟲略奪港人資產。<br />\n<br />\n校巴司機不惜犧牲自己完成愛港大業！應封為北角烈士！<br />\n<br />\n大家請起立，敬禮！"},{"pid":"96820cf7afd9ba1e7b827d404018d6906aa94292","tid":936511,"uid":10637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T23:16:36.000Z","msg":"Post依個去discuss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755b1b53630a2d03007b25c27ae3ca6170b8fd1d","tid":936511,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T23:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Post依個去discuss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有勞巴打。<br />\n<br />\n小弟無discuss accc"},{"pid":"038597665cc239a3ae879c3420662d7f794bd5c0","tid":936511,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T23:19:01.000Z","msg":"口德村全面進場"},{"pid":"c3460e1389138a9171a858cb09f9ee118fad1c40","tid":936511,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T23:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d087fb67b88ce74e45c9917819193edab377207d","tid":936511,"uid":124282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T23:53:58.000Z","msg":"我明明見焦土話要投建制派<br />\n<br />\n60席都係建制，等港豬覺醒ga wor"},{"pid":"39b2aabd348a4b8f8bcfdfc7b7d5a4e88b5e5208","tid":936511,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T00